'''''Sinking Sands''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Gana]] yo mu 2010,<ref>SINKING SANDS | AFRICAN MOVIE REVIEW | Talk African Movies</ref> yanditswe yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Leila Djansi, ikinwamo Jimmy Jean-Louis, Ama Abebrese, Emmanuel Yeboah A. na Yemi Blaq<ref>Through Sinking Sands - Nigeriafilms.com <nowiki>https://www.nigeriafilms.com</nowiki> › ... › Film/TV Workshop</ref> . Iyi filime yakiriye ibihembo icyenda  kandi yatsindiye ibihembo 3 muri Afurika ya Movie Academy Awards 2011, harimo ibihembo bya ''Best Screenplay'' & ''Best Makeup'' <ref>Sinking Sands | Nollywood Forever Movie Reviews <nowiki>http://nollywoodforever.com</nowiki> › sinking-sands</ref><ref>Tag: Sinking Sands - Ghana Film Industry <nowiki>https://www.ghanafilmindustry.com</nowiki> › tag › sinking-sands</ref>. 

== Ikibanza ==
Iyi filime ivuga amateka y'abashakanye, Jimah na Pabi, ishyingiranwa ryabo rikaba urugomo no guhohoterwa iyo Jimah ahindutse isura mu mpanuka yo mu rugo<ref>Ghanaian Born Award Winning Director, Leila Djansi's Hit ... <nowiki>https://face2faceafrica.com</nowiki> › article › ghanaian-born-a...</ref>. 

== Kwakira ==
Iyi filime yakiriwe neza nabantu benshi banenga firime nyafurika hamwe na NollywoodForever.com basoza bavuga ko "Filime nziza nabatura mbikuye ku mutima<ref>Sinking Sands Hits Nollywood Cinema | Movies - Peace FM <nowiki>https://www.peacefmonline.com</nowiki> › pages › showbiz › m...</ref>. Ibi birerekana abo bantu bose bafite ibitekerezo bigufi bizera ko ukeneye glitz, glamour na brazilian kuboha kugirango ukore firime nziza utakora<ref>Leila Djansi's Sinking Sands Makes it to CNN As Must-see ... <nowiki>https://www.nydjlive.com</nowiki> › leila-djansis-sinking-sands-...</ref>. Ubukorikori muri firime bwari buteye ubwoba no gushimwa. Gukina byari ingingo nkuko byari bimeze kuri sinema.<ref>Sinking Sands - Alchetron, The Free Social Encyclopedia <nowiki>https://alchetron.com</nowiki> › Sinking-Sands</ref> "
